      <h2 class="h2">Coffee4Craig</h2>
      <p>Coffee4Craig provides an evening drop-in service supporting people experiencing homelessness. We do this by providing home-cooked meals, access to a medic, a shower and barbering service, advice – and a team of friendly staff and volunteers.</p>
      <a href="https://news.streetsupport.net/2023/11/12/spotlight-coffee4craig/">Learn more about Coffee4Craig</a>
