      <h2 class="h2">Engage, Grow, Go</h2>
      <p>EGG (or Engage, Grow, Go) is a Manchester and Stockport-based charity, offering homelessness support throughout the North West. We look at the long-term solution, helping people out of homelessness, into their own homes and either work or self-employment. </p>
      <a href="https://news.streetsupport.net/2023/11/12/spotlight-engage-grow-go/">Learn more about Engage, Grow, Go</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

