      <h2 class="h2">Greater Together Manchester</h2>
      <p>Greater Together Manchester is an anti-poverty charity supporting and empowering people in Greater Manchester. We work primarily with people who have experience of homelessness and other related difficulties. We run various projects including a Social Super Market, our Befriending Service, Wayfinder, and our activities programme Lifeskills.</p>
      <a href="https://news.streetsupport.net/2023/11/12/spotlight-greater-together-manchester/">Learn more about Greater Together Manchester</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="block">
