      <img class="vol-for-good-logo" src="/assets/img/vfg-imgs/independent-choices.png" alt="">
      <h2 class="h2">Independent Choices</h2>
      <p>Independent Choices Greater Manchester set up our confidential Greater Manchester Domestic Abuse Helpline in 1978. It is open for anyone over the age of 16 who is experiencing or has previously experienced domestic abuse & violence in any form. Crucially, our Helpline can also be accessed by professionals, as well as friends and family who want to support loved ones.  </p>
      <a href="https://news.streetsupport.net/2023/11/12/spotlight-independent-choices/">Learn more about Independent Choices</a>
    </div>
