      <h2 class="h2">Other places to look for volunteering opportunities</h2>
      <p>If none of our featured organisations suit you, it could be that you’re not in Greater Manchester, or you’d like to look outside the homelessness sector, there are still plenty of options.</p>
      <p>We’d suggest researching charities near you and contacting them directly. Perhaps you’re particularly passionate about their mission, perhaps their values align well with your own. We’d also recommend making sure they’re a registered charity, for your safety as well as those you’d be working with.</p>
      <p>If you’re still curious about the sorts of roles out there, these are the job boards we recommend having a look through.</p><br>
